    // counts; 6.2.B adds repair-priority; 6.2.C1 adds receive-delivery;
    // 6.2.F adds supply / fuel inspection; 6.2.G adds transfer-to-other-
    // hangar. State hangars are baseline-staffed: the BT find-job path
    // claims the seat naturally (NPC-only, no requirements, no installOnly).
